      {
        "id": "Extension",
        "path": "Extension",
        "short": "NDH Delivery Method",
        "definition": "This extension enables NDH to declare how a service is delivered and, when virtual, which modalities are supported, using structured sub-extensions and ValueSet bindings to DeliveryMethodVS and VirtualModalitiesVS for predictable service-access routing; it is used in HealthcareService."
